\cf0 Mandatory is a full font developed from the typeface used for UK vehicle registration plates. There is improved stroke separation on the M and W which are pointed at the centre.\
\
Mandatory has been designed to conform to the required proportions \'96\
\
Height \'96\'a0 790 units\
Character width \'96 500 units (except 1 and I)\
Stroke \'96 140 units\
Sidebearings \'96 2 x 55 units (Letter spaces \'96 110 units)\
Word/Group Space \'96 330 units
